<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-683] Lazy Field Loading has edge case bug causing read past EOF</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-683</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;While trying to run some benchmarking of Lazy filed loading, i discovered there seems to be an edge case when accessing the last field of the last doc of an index.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the problem seems to only happen when the doc has been accessed after at least one other doc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i have not tried to dig into the code to find the root cause, testcase to follow...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
